  "description": "A stunning sunset over a coastal city and harbor. The sun, a bright orange orb, is partially obscured by wispy clouds, creating a dramatic sky filled with warm hues of orange, yellow, and hints of red. Below the vibrant sky lies a city sprawling along the coastline, with buildings and infrastructure visible in silhouette. A calm sea stretches into the distance, punctuated by a breakwater and a few distant ships. Lush green vegetation frames the lower left corner of the image, adding depth and a natural element to the scene. The overall impression is one of tranquility and natural beauty.",
